        <div class="col div_center ">
            <h2>Menu</h2>
            <img class="img_Logos divs2" src="~/images/MenuLogo_HP.png" />

            <br />
            <a class="btn btn-secondary " asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Menu">Order Here</a>
            <br />
            <br />
            <br />
            <h2>Stories</h2>
            <img class="img_Logos divs2" src="~/images/HistoryLogo_HP.png" />

            <br />

            <p>
                See what's cooking at Notaburger,
                Discover opportunities at the restaurants,
                including the latest stories, news, and events.
                home office, and in the field.
            </p>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Stories"><i class="fa-solid fa-newspaper"></i>  Learn More</a>
            <br />


        </div>
        <div class="col div_center">
            <h2 class="text-center">Rewards</h2>
            <img class="img_Logos divs2" src="~/images/RewardsLogo_HP.png" />

            <br />
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Stories">Learn More</a>
            <br />
            <br />
            <br />
            <h2 class="text-center">Community</h2>
            <img class="img_Logos divs2" src="~/images/CommunityLogo_HP.png" />
            <p>Keep up to date what is happening in <strong> YOUR </strong> town! Check what changes your local NotABurgers are doing to keep your community safe and connected.</p>


        </div>
        <div class="div_center">
            <h2 class="text-center">Careers</h2>
            <img class="img_Logos center_img divs2" style="width: 220px" src="~/images/CareersLogo_HP.png" />
